# API Reference (Auto-Generated)

This directory contains auto-generated API documentation created by TypeDoc.

## Generating Documentation

To regenerate the API documentation:

```bash
pnpm docs:build
```

This will parse all TypeScript source files and JSDoc comments to create comprehensive HTML documentation.

## Viewing Documentation

### Option 1: Local HTTP Server

```bash
pnpm docs:serve
```

Then open http://localhost:8000 in your browser.

### Option 2: Open Directly

Open `docs/api/index.html` in your web browser.

## Notes

- This directory is git-ignored (see `.gitignore`)
- API documentation should be regenerated whenever public APIs change
- Consider adding `pnpm docs:build` to the pre-publish workflow

## Source

Documentation is generated from:
- `packages/cli/src/**/*.ts`
- `packages/config/src/**/*.ts`
- `packages/core/src/**/*.ts`
- `packages/extractors/src/**/*.ts`
- `packages/git/src/**/*.ts`

Test files and internal implementations are excluded.
